video.title: Dicte
video.synopsis: A crime reporter starts a new life by returning to her hometown, where she finds herself at odds with the police when she tries to solve their cases.

episodes.synopsis: Dicte finds the body of a young woman who died of a C-section. Due to this macabre find, Dicte gets to know Inspector Wagner.
episodes.title: Personal - Part 1

episodes.synopsis: Dicte finds the body of a young woman who died of a C-section. Due to this macabre find, Dicte gets to know Inspector Wagner.

episodes.synopsis: One summer night, Dicte sees a burning cart in the driveway of her neighbors. Inside the house, Inger Gravgård seems to have committed suicide.

episodes.synopsis: A bath tub with the corpse of a newborn floats in the harbor. Dicte goes with her gut but Wagner warns her not to jump to conclusions.

episodes.synopsis: After years of silence, Dicte's father finally reaches out to her. But before he can share his vital news, fate intervenes.
episodes.title: Dreams and Diamonds - Part 1

episodes.synopsis: The suspect in the speeding car turns out to be someone unexpected, and has a connection to murder victim Tiffany.
episodes.title: Dreams and Diamonds - Part 2

episodes.synopsis: After a wellness maven is found dead in S&M bondage, Dicte and Wagner investigate several likely male suspects and look for a secret lover.

episodes.synopsis: Dicte uncovers a new line of investigation in the sadomasochistic murder of Lotte Askov and takes a bold risk that could cost the journalist her life.
episodes.title: Passion and Chains - Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Dicte and Wagner go on high alert after a provocative 12-year-old with a rebellious streak mysteriously disappears from a teen party.
episodes.title: Presence and Absence - Part 1

episodes.synopsis: As he investigates the disappearance of a missing 12-year-old, Wagner concludes that she's been kidnapped and follows the clues to a mink farm.
episodes.title: Presence and Absence - Part 2

episodes.synopsis: Dicte, Torsten and Rose attend a local soccer match to cheer on Rose's beau, who's the star of the team. But a deadly fight interrupts the action.
episodes.title: Goals and Means - Part 1

episodes.synopsis: After writing a damning exposé about match-fixing, Dicte is threatened but refuses to back down and continues her search for the killer.
episodes.title: Goals and Means - Part 2

episodes.synopsis: As he is contacting Dicte, Wagner finds a shocking scene. Dicte realizes that Wagner was involved with the fugitive and had hidden her from the law.

episodes.synopsis: Implicated by the evidence, Wagner is accused of two murders. After his arrest, Dicte visits him in jail and slips him a surprise.
